     H            Y.
     F** ALHRC0 **********************************
     F* LOQ INPROCESS SCAN RESULT FILE           *
     F*    MAEDA.                2017.08.08      *
     F********************************************
     FALHPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FALHWP01 O   F     256            DISK                      A
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A1SKHZ
     I                                        1   40A1SKYY
     I                                        5   60A1SKMM
     I                                        7   80A1SKDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A1SCHZ
     I                                        1   40A1SCYY
     I                                        5   60A1SCMM
     I                                        7   80A1SCDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WDATE
     I                                        1   60STIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
     I                                        7  100SDAYY
     I                                       11  120SDAMM
     I                                       13  140SDADD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80@DATE
     I                                        1   40@DAYY
     I                                        5   60@DAMM
     I                                        7   80@DADD
      *
     C                     TIME           WDATE
      *１ヶ月前
     C                     Z-ADDSDATE     @DATE
     C           @DAMM     IFEQ 1
     C                     SUB  1         @DAYY
     C                     Z-ADD12        @DAMM
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SUB  1         @DAMM
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KEYA11    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @DAYY
     C                     KFLD           @DAMM
     C                     KFLD           @DADD
      *
     C                     MOVEL'000'     WWCO2P  3
     C           KEYA11    SETLLALHPL03
     C                     READ ALHPL03                  83
     C           *IN83     DOWEQ'0'
     C           A1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           A1SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W@RONO  3
     C                     MOVELA1OQNO    W@RONO
     C                     Z-ADDA1TSQ#    W@TSQ#  40
     C                     EXCPTDAT
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ ALHPL03                  83
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     OALHWP01 EADD             DAT
     O                         A1SERL    12
     O                         A1OQNO    14
     O                         A1SHN1    20
     O                         A1SHN2    25
     O                         A1SHN3    27
     O                         A1ZACD    30
     O                         A1ZANM    45
     O                         A1HOJI    47
     O                         A1ONDO    50
     O                         WWCO2P    53
     O*                        A1CO2P    53
     O                         W@TSQ#    57
     O                         A1SCYY    61
     O                         A1SCMM    63
     O                         A1SCDD    65
     O                         A1SCTM    71
